            <p>Four weight primitives defined in the <strong>Type primitives</strong> collection. All three typeface modes support these weights.</p>

            <div class="collection-badge">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M4 7V4h16v3M9 20h6M12 4v16"/></svg>
